debconf-translation-manager (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * GTK4/Adwaita rewrite with sidebar navigation (GNOME Settings style)
  * Sidebar with icon buttons: Packages, Editor, Statistics, Settings
  * Statistics view with colorful Cairo pie and bar charts
  * Inline settings panel (no separate window)
  * PO editor with jump-to-untranslated/fuzzy navigation
  * Removed requests/beautifulsoup4 dependencies (uses urllib)
  * Entry point: debconf-translation-manager (console_scripts)

 -- Daniel Nylander <daniel@danielnylander.se>  Thu, 06 Mar 2026 11:00:00 +0100

debconf-translation-manager (0.7.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Complete rewrite with workflow-based NavigationView UI
  * PackageListPage: sortable, searchable, color-coded untranslated packages
  * PackageDetailPage: download PO, translate, lint, submit actions
  * PoEditorPage: side-by-side msgid/msgstr, fuzzy highlighting
  * SubmitDialog: one-click email with standard Debian l10n format
  * StatsPage: SQLite history, language rankings, CSV export
  * Settings: language, SMTP, Gmail preset
  * Swedish translation 100%

 -- Daniel Nylander <daniel@danielnylander.se>  Thu, 06 Mar 2026 09:11:00 +0100
